<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
        }

        header, footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        main {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-section {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 3rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #444;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .team-section {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .team-member {
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin: 1rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            width: 250px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .team-member img {
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .team-member h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .team-member p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #777;
        }

        footer p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Include Header -->
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main>
        <section class="about-section">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>We are a team of passionate individuals dedicated to delivering high-quality courses and content to empower learners globally. Our mission is to provide accessible, affordable, and effective education to help users develop valuable skills and knowledge.</p>
            <p>With years of experience in the industry, our team strives to create an enriching learning experience by offering a variety of courses that cater to different fields and interests.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Team Section -->
        <section class="team-section">
            <div class="team-member">
                <img src="/images/member1.jpg" alt="Team Member 1">
                <h3>John Doe</h3>
                <p>Lead Instructor</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member">
                <img src="/images/member2.jpg" alt="Team Member 2">
                <h3>Jane Smith</h3>
                <p>Content Strategist</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member">
                <img src="/images/member3.jpg" alt="Team Member 3">
                <h3>Michael Lee</h3>
                <p>Course Developer</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <!-- Include Footer -->
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
